title: Assessing Flood Risk and Urban Expansion: A Case Study of Mandalay, Myanmar
text:
Author: Sihan Yu
Date: November 2025
This notebook presents a demonstration of flood risk assessment and urban land use analysis using open-source geospatial tools.
It uses placeholder data and illustrative examples to showcase methods for hydrological modeling, land classification, and flood extent visualization.
